<bibRefCitation author="Rajan, K. C. &amp; Nair, N. B." box="[711,943,941,966]" pageId="8" pageNumber="503" pagination="180 - 182" refId="ref9978" refString="Rajan, K. C. &amp; Nair, N. B. (1979) Colonization of graded sand by the interstitial fauna of Monazite sands. Indian Journal of Marine Science, 8, 180 - 182." type="journal article" year="1979">Rajan &amp; Nair (1979)</bibRefCitation>
